==Hindi==
===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''वह''' (vaha)

# [[that]] - direct case only, see below for oblique. (Plural: [[वे]])
#:Example: "वह मकान बड़ा है" - That house is large
# [[he]] - direct case only, far reference. (If [[respect]] is conveyed, वे is used)
#:Example: "वह छोटा है" - He is small
# [[she]] - direct case only, far reference. (If [[respect]] is conveyed, वे is used)
#:Example "वह छोटी है" - She is small
# [[it]] - direct case only.

====Inflection====
[[Oblique]]: [[उस]]

